description: Discover this exquisite 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo nestled in the heart of South Boston. This stylish unit offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience, with stunning features and a prime location. Sleek kitchen with custom cabinetry and quartz countertops, modern, energy-efficient appliances. The open-concept living room and kitchen create a seamless flow, perfect for entertaining. The kitchen slider opens to a Juliet balcony, allowing natural light to flood the space, cozy up by the gas fireplace on chilly evenings. Enjoy the beauty hardwood floors throughout the entire condo. Indulge in the luxurious master bedroom featuring an ensuite bathroom and a spacious walk-in closet & The second bedroom is well-lit and offers ample closet space. Stackable washer and dryer are tucked away in the laundry closet. Private storage space is available in the basement. Your dedicated off-street parking space is conveniently located. Walk across the street to a serene beach and watch the boats.
